{"word":"βασανιστέος","slug":"βασανιστέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βασανιστέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> from <a href='S:βασανίζω'><el>βασανίζω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be put to the proof</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>βασανιστέον</el> <i>one must put to the torture</i>, <el>τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}